{"type": "article", "id": 13236, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-10T08:14:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 14234, "name": "洗手盆"}, {"id": 9968, "name": "手机壳"}, {"id": 14235, "name": "胶囊旅馆"}, {"id": 2209, "name": "餐具"}, {"id": 9230, "name": "哆啦A梦"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122455Rxp8XAq45BfhEyvL.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tNew Furniture Collection by Greycork\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最近来自罗德岛的家具设计公司 Greycork 推出了新的家具系列，这个公司成立于 2014 年，一直号称要做比 IKEA “更加便于组装，更加平板包装”的家具。新的产品线包括一个沙发，一个躺椅，一个书架，一个咖啡桌和一个边桌，所有的家具都采用平板包装，目标是任何人在 4 分钟内组装好。而设计上也走的极简风格。目前在 Indiegogo 上可以支持预定，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102728JIuX1UkLaF4l7yZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102728qRZdJ7CGw145zYVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102728WigD35Cu7RJ9PbaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102729bZ92l6tLoOQkHNjy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102729y9ZsJq0uDYBKFeIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027306ebkhg3xLcE9jG2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102731pDBAkP64xtbai87K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027315ZO7URyd3mx9MguJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tObvious Table Lamp by Jordi Rizo\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“折纸”一直是很多设计师感兴趣的概念，于是我们常常看到许多折纸式的设计。巴塞罗那设计工作室 Obvious 最近推出了一款折纸式的台灯，灯身采用的是不锈钢材料，灯光亮起来时，光影的变化会让整个灯看起来非常美丽。这是<a href=\"https://www.barcelonaindesign.com/designer/obvious/\" target=\"_blank\">设计工作室的主页</a>，他们致力于用常见的材料做简单的日常物件，走极简风格，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027319RHnEYoclyOVZJUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102732Tuz5PDhOac0bkGrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102732VAfYGgRt84oaFWyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027324pO5txw1DF7J0Uuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tDoraemon Collection by DING DONG \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>今年哆啦 A 梦主题周边真是目不暇接呀。来自香港的 DING DONG 在近日推出了一大波与哆啦 A 梦的联名系列，包括时光机主题浮床、铜锣烧飞盘、哆啦 A 梦冰格、纸胶带、徽章等等。另外，“DING DONG” 的名字灵感据说来自门铃声，象征顾客收到产品时候的喜悦心情。<span>这是<a href=\"http://www.dingdongtakuhaibin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140821xOWX8DksZYcFSqpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140822yZnV2rKkaeIRS3jQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140822C76PoRiM1Kmpwsh9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140823ETA4fYZ2ns6vL5JX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140824CRA4JqnftS82iu7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140825cXvwmbDVOKl7rnxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140825JEWk2G4rUVcpwLg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140826p0dvfiuW32T8hKQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140826hHLyGKNEwrtI0xDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140827RkjbNlM6XWxi5Fea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tiPhone Case by MTV &amp; Ampfly\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>近日，MTV 和 Ampfly 联手推出了一款 iPhone 保护套，不同于普通保护套的是，它能够在不使用任何电源或电子设备的情况下，完全依靠保护套外观的设计形状，使得手机的音量达到正常情况下的 3 倍，同时在低音领域也保持了一定水准。颜色上目前有黑、白、红、蓝四种可选择，同时，你还可以通过在上面刻字，制作自己个性化的保护套。这是<a href=\"http://ampflysound.com/products/iphone-6-case-red\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102733aNUInSMy2PvJHAlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102733kqr2Xj96pGblW0U3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102734dzwloIZCb6PG2L4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102735gE9qOJTKrwQDv1jH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tTritensil by Map Studio\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>英国设计工作室 Map Studio 为百货公司 Fortnum &amp; Mason 设计了一款特殊的餐具，把刀、叉和勺子三种功能结合在一起。其灵感来自一战时期士兵们使用的一种类似的工具，设计初衷是方便人们外带食物时使用方便，叉子用于搅拌沙拉，勺子适合吃甜品，而锯齿刀可以进行简单的切割和搅拌，而不会伤到嘴。他们表示多种功能合为一体，可以减少二氧化碳量。产品有塑料和不锈钢两种材料可以选择。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102735A09FMIz5glT6PnEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027355suQv2pDr8JlSk0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102735ZNm5OR2cg0XGsU6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102736wZdOUeNhvmAnaEQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021027369p7nIezQX6OhiySH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102737VUsFelZTru9vIyhC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102737tv3Pxdep5aY6TN0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102737ATpGiyeuCc4Q1KqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102738Om2ouqBrylxKsw9v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tBusiness Class Capsule Hotels by First Cabin \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>日本的胶囊旅馆小巧但精致，各种设施应有尽有，而且价格也往往比较可爱。最近，First Cabin 推出了一套“商务舱”胶囊旅馆，房间更为宽敞，装潢也更加精致，除了普通的设施之外，还设有咖啡厅和酒吧等娱乐场所。而价格也十分厚道，大部分在 5000 日元左右，这是<a href=\"http://first-cabin.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">预定地址</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102738VOWGukTQsAMlLXyc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102739mb0MwKpnQ9drvVjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102739FduDZKsXUtnehH1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102740mR9g4YJtQaxhMezU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210274039FAIw8geHl4PtaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102740n5rdROyHIbVkSmMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102741ghMVQc5EzSPxDO3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}